originalText.text: Dr. Bell was knowledgeable, very thorough and took the time to address my concerns. The office is very nice with a convenient location and a friendly, helpful staff. I highly recommend Dr. Bell.

originalText.text: What a great doctor! I feel very lucky to have Dr. Ryan Bell, MD on my side. He is always available when I need him or have a question. Dr. Bell is polite, friendly, professional and most importantly he cares about your wellness. I usually find something to complain about but with Dr. Bell I cannot find anything. A+ all around.

originalText.text: Dr. Bell was extremely patient and attentive. The office was extremely clean and well maintained. I arrived 15 minutes before my appointment and was seen within 10 min of arriving which was still before my appointment time. The front desk staff were all extremely welcoming, courteous, and helpful. Will definitely recommend this office.
